OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777223159
OL,3,CPolice investigate video that seems to
OL,4,Cshow player punch fan
OL,6,FPolice are investigating a video which
OL,7,Fappears to show a York player punching
OL,8,Fa fan after the team clinched
OL,9,Fpromotion away from Rochdale back to
OL,10,Fthe Football League for the first time
OL,11,Fin a decade.
OL,13,FThe win followed a frantic few minutes
OL,14,Fof stoppage-time drama which saw two
OL,15,Fgoals and a number of fan pitch
OL,16,Finvasions, where York City claimed the
OL,17,Fpoint they needed from a 1-1 draw to
OL,18,Fwin the title in the 13th minute of
OL,19,Fstoppage-time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
