PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777223159
OL,3,CPolice investigate video that seems to
OL,4,Cshow player punch fan
OL,6,FHowever, during the second of two
OL,7,Fpitch invasions - the first which saw
OL,8,FRochdale fans storm on to the pitch
OL,9,Fafter Emmanuel Dieseruvwe had put them
OL,10,Fahead ` a recording began circulating
OL,11,Fonline which appears to show a
OL,12,Fconfrontation between a fan and a York
OL,13,Fplayer, who was on his knees at the
OL,14,Ffinal whistle.
OL,16,FAs stewards attempted to separate the
OL,17,Fpair, the player gets to his feet and
OL,18,Fappears to punch the fan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
