OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777223159
OL,3,CPolice investigate video that seems to
OL,4,Cshow player punch fan
OL,6,F"We are aware of a video that is
OL,7,Fcirculating of a possible assault
OL,8,Finvolving a player and we have linked
OL,9,Fin with both clubs and the National
OL,10,FLeague," Greater Manchester Police
OL,11,Fsaid in a statement.
OL,13,F"We will be further assessing the
OL,14,Fvideo and reviewing CCTV of the
OL,15,Fincident."
OL,17,FA total of four Rochdale fans were
OL,18,Farrested, one on suspicion of assault
OL,19,Fand pitch incursion, one on suspicion
OL,20,Fof a public order offence and two on
OL,21,Fsuspicion of pitch incursion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]uD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
