OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777223159
OL,3,CPolice investigate video that seems to
OL,4,Cshow player punch fan
OL,6,FA York supporter was also arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of assault and police
OL,8,Fconfirmed he would be interviewed at a
OL,9,Flater date.
OL,11,FBoth Rochdale and York have been
OL,12,Fapproached for comment.
OL,14,FYork only needed to avoid defeat on
OL,15,FSaturday but they fell behind when
OL,16,FDieseruvwe headed home in the fifth
OL,17,Fminute of injury time and had Rochdale
OL,18,Fheld on, they would have guaranteed a
OL,19,Fplace in League Two next season.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
