OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777223159
OL,3,CPolice investigate video that seems to
OL,4,Cshow player punch fan
OL,6,FHowever, Stones' dramatic equaliser
OL,7,Fmeans Dale will have to focus on the
OL,8,Fplay-offs, with York now looking
OL,9,Ftowards being back in the EFL next
OL,10,Fseason for the first time since 2016.
OL,12,F"I think it was written in the stars,"
OL,13,FYork manager Stuart Maynard said on
OL,14,FYork's X account. "The football gods
OL,15,Fwere with us and we're just buzzing to
OL,16,Fget over the line.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@fO]vD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
