OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777223159
OL,3,CPolice investigate video that seems to
OL,4,Cshow player punch fan
OL,6,F"There's a real belief within this
OL,7,Fgroup. The one thing me and
OL,8,F(assistant) Joao (Alves) have
OL,9,Finstalled at this football club is we
OL,10,Fshow no disappointment, we keep going
OL,11,Fall the way. Until the end and until
OL,12,Fit's over, it's never over."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@\O]
